    <item>
      <title>软银将投资人工智能初创公司 Perplexity，估值达 30 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/softbank-to-invest-in-perplexity-in-ai-race-against-google-rivals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[软银集团旗下的愿景基金 2 号正在以 30 亿美元的估值投资美国人工智能初创公司 Perplexity AI，这是孙正义对该领域的最新押注，他认为该领域对于确保自己的遗产至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/softbank-to-invest-in-perplexity-in-ai-race-against-google-rivals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 04:07:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊计划推出折扣网店以对抗 Temu、Shein</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-27/amazon-plans-discount-web-store-to-counter-china-s-temu-shein</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司计划推出一个在线商店，销售从中国直接发货的低价服装和家居用品。这家总部位于西雅图的电子商务巨头旨在对抗 Temu 和 Shein 等折扣新贵的崛起。Annabelle Droulers 在彭博电视台报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-27/amazon-plans-discount-web-store-to-counter-china-s-temu-shein</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 03:57:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SpaceX 的投标报价据称将使该公司估值达到创纪录的 2100 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/spacex-tender-offer-said-to-value-company-at-record-210-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，SpaceX 将通过招标方式以每股 112 美元的价格出售内部人士股份，这一高于预期的价格将使埃隆马斯克的太空和卫星公司的价值接近 2100 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/spacex-tender-offer-said-to-value-company-at-record-210-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 03:32:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美光的抛售凸显了人工智能预期过高的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/micron-s-selloff-shows-risk-of-sky-high-ai-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美光科技公司业绩公布后的抛售再次提醒全球投资者，投资人工智能芯片制造商存在一定风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/micron-s-selloff-shows-risk-of-sky-high-ai-expectations</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 02:26:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>现代汽车寻求更多电动汽车改装，推出售价低于 25,000 欧元的 Inster City 汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/hyundai-seeks-more-ev-converts-with-sub-25-000-inster-city-car</link>
      <description><![CDATA[现代汽车公司正加入试图加速电动汽车普及、抵御来自中国的低成本竞争的汽车制造商行列，推出一款电池供电的车型，据称其售价将低于 25,000 欧元（26,775 美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/hyundai-seeks-more-ev-converts-with-sub-25-000-inster-city-car</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
